come back next week.

283
00:18:52,710 --> 00:18:54,150
I wanted to come earlier.

284
00:18:54,810 --> 00:18:57,070
Without grandma there,
I was kind of…

285
00:18:57,810 --> 00:18:58,970
lost.

286
00:18:59,670 --> 00:19:01,040
Right?

287
00:19:02,830 --> 00:19:04,830
