375
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:44,090
Theo!

376
00:26:44,350 --> 00:26:45,600
Theo.

377
00:26:45,600 --> 00:26:47,770
I missed you so much.

378
00:26:48,070 --> 00:26:49,560
Come here.

379
00:26:53,240 --> 00:26:54,730
I missed you.
Can I get a kiss?

380
00:26:55,520 --> 00:26:57,870
