382
00:26:59,040 --> 00:27:00,860
so it wouldn't be tiring for you.

383
00:27:02,910 --> 00:27:05,550
Hello.

384
00:27:06,050 --> 00:27:07,770
So how was last night?

385
00:27:07,770 --> 00:27:09,060
You spent the night
at Akk's place, right?

386
00:27:09,060 --> 00:27:10,040
I did.

387
00:27:11,640 --> 00:27:12,940
