dinner with his parents.

541
00:37:03,130 --> 00:37:04,770
Their beloved
son is back after all.

542
00:37:05,090 --> 00:37:06,240
Try calling him.

543
00:37:14,960 --> 00:37:15,950
Yes, Por?

544
00:37:16,550 --> 00:37:17,400
Akk.

545
00:37:17,400 --> 00:37:18,790
Are you free tonight?

546
00:37:18,790 --> 00:37:20,460
M just called in sick.

547
00:37:20,590 --> 00:37:23,900
He was supposed to develop films
after the shop is closed tonight.

548
00:37:23,900 --> 00:37:25,370
This job should be done ages ago.

549
00:37:25,370 --> 00:37:27,420
Many of them are due tomorrow.

550
00:37:27,420 --> 00:37:28,250
Can you come instead?

551
00:37:28,250 --> 00:37:29,830
I just got home.

552
00:37:29,830 --> 00:37:32,150
